不想活了，便自行擊碎天靈蓋，空見立即躍將過來，伸手架開謝遜右掌，謝遜左手發「七傷拳」拳擊出打在空見胸腹之間，空見全無提防，連運神功的念頭也沒生，空見血肉之軀登時內臟震裂，摔倒在地。"},{"pid":"27cf982da0c4d853eeff42b362a48a45b417f6d4","tid":1305823,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"929323231057cd2c6781c0be33b56a1b32f11e12","tid":1305823,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"世清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:31:45.000Z","msg":"樓主又消費世清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0d7596df8062226401f2d6a5760d428ce60901","tid":1305823,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"個肥佬好型"},{"pid":"ac78f46e7e3e09f6d8b567965b37db6bbb58faa7","tid":1305823,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"呢個社會唔容許持槍 <br />\n所以世清先練肌肉<br />\n就算你有槍 <br />\n你都唔夠世清d肌肉快"},{"pid":"111f6b96bd2c55f4cdd9b995826eda8deb62ca19","tid":1305823,"uid":22589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"肉酸收皮啦 係狗竇柒左出黎吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71dc53cff3a091b25ff4e1b10092158a97adb1d6","tid":1305823,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27cf982da0c4d853eeff42b362a48a45b417f6d4","tid":1305823,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"929323231057cd2c6781c0be33b56a1b32f11e12","tid":1305823,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"世清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:31:45.000Z","msg":"樓主又消費世清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfe72742fdeda140d8c0915db5eedc6814fc657","tid":1305823,